works.description: Individually and luxuriously designed, the Continental motorhome from the house of Ketterer Spezialfahrzeuge AG is truly a home away from home. The Ketterer Continental motorhome combines compact length with spacious and luxurious living. Perfectly created living space, cabins and salons, a strategic layout in two versions and amazing lounge atmosphere make this motorhome an extraordinary home away from home. The Ketterer Continental features a spacious living room with dining and kitchen area, a bathroom with large washstand
